      <description>&lt;h1 id=&#34;intelligent-agents&#34;&gt;Intelligent Agents&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Agents are objects with attitude, which are autonomous, smart, active.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;properties-in-environment-环境性质描述&#34;&gt;Properties in Environment (环境性质描述)&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fully observable / partially observable&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deterministic / non-deterministic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Static / dynamic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Discrete / continuous&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Episodic / non-episodic&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Real time&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;social-ability-社交能力&#34;&gt;Social ability (社交能力)&lt;/h2&gt;
